FORMAT: 1A
HOST: https://trade-ninjas.herokuapp.com/

# Trade-Ninjas

Trade Ninjas is a simple APi that provides access to trading indicators and chart patterns


## Set Cookies [/cookies]

### Initialize all cookies [POST]

To set the cookies make a post request on the above URL


+ Response 201 (application/json)

        {
            "message": "Cookies have been set"
        }


## View all Indicators [/indicators]

### List all available indicators [GET]

You can recieve a list of all available indicators


+ Request (application/json)


       
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "1": "bollinger",
            "2": "MACD",
            "3": "RSI"
        }
        

## View all Candlestick patterns [/patterns]

### List all available candlestick patterns [GET]

You can recieve a list of all available candlestick patterns


+ Request (application/json)


       
       
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "1": "doji",
            "2": "threeblackcrows",
            "3": "threewhitesoldiers"
        }
         
         
