## View candlestick pattern [/patterns/<string:patternname>]

### View pattern [GET]

You can recieve a boolean indicating if a pattern is present


+ Request (application/json)


    + Headers

            Cookie: doji
       
       
+ Response 200 (application/json)


        {
            "dojiPattern": "true"
        }